rows.label: qst000106_msg002
rows.name:
Because you drove off the
Trent Krabbles, I was able
to deliver the cargo safely.

rows.label: qst000106_msg003
rows.name:
You were a great help.
I'm in your debt.

rows.label: qst000106_msg004
rows.name:
If I had someone as skilled
as you guarding me, things
would be a little easier, but[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst000106_msg006
rows.name:
If I'm attacked by Trent Krabbles
again, I'll try requesting help
from the Hræsvelgr Mercenaries.

rows.label: qst000106_msg007
rows.name:
I hear all the mercenaries
there are quite skilled.

rows.label: qst000106_msg008
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Ah, I got sidetracked. Let
me give you a reward for
protecting the cargo.
